Text:
Tahun ni nak cari tempat buka puasa yang tak perlu beratur masa nak makan. 

Aku tak suka buffet ramadan sebab kena bersesak-sesak beratur nak ambik makanan. Kita dah la penat puasa seharian lapar & dahaga, bayar mahal pulak tu lepastu nak kena beratur.
Translated_Tweets:
This year I want to find a fast -paced place that doesn't have to be in time to eat.

I don't like the Ramadan buffet because I have to be in a hurry to get some food. We are tired of fasting all day hungry & amp; thirst, pay expensive then you want to get in line.
